<pclass="MsoNormal"align="left"style="text-align:left;line-height:20.0pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><spanstyle="font-family:
宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2014.8至9&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新加坡国立大学&nbsp;&nbsp;高级研究助理
<pclass="MsoNormal"align="left"style="text-align:left;line-height:20.0pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><spanstyle="font-family:
宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2012.2至2012.8&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新加坡国立大学&nbsp;访问学者&nbsp;
<pclass="MsoNormal"align="left"style="text-align:left;line-height:20.0pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><spanlang="EN-US"style="font-family:宋体;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;2008.07<spanstyle="font-family:
宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;">至2011.9&nbsp;&nbsp;新加坡国立大学&nbsp;助理研究员
<pclass="MsoNormal"align="left"style="text-align:left;line-height:20.0pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><spanlang="EN-US"style="font-family:宋体;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;2010.04-2010.06&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;">瑞典乌普沙拉大学&nbsp;访问学者
<pclass="MsoNormal"align="left"style="text-align:left;line-height:20.0pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><spanlang="EN-US"style="font-family:宋体;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;2009.04-2009.06&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<spanstyle="font-family:宋体;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;">澳大利亚皇家墨尔本理工大学&nbsp;访问学者
<pclass="MsoNormal"align="left"style="text-align:left;line-height:20.0pt;
mso-line-height-rule:exactly"><spanlang="EN-US"style="font-family:宋体;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;2003.09<spanstyle="font-family:
